Class PatternMatcher

java.lang.Object
  org.neo4j.graphmatching.PatternMatcher
Deprecated. 

@Deprecated
public class PatternMatcher
extends Object

The PatternMatcher is the engine that performs the matching of a graph pattern with the actual graph.
